    Locus: III
    Title: Vinaya-Pitaka
Tags:
  - Discernment-Truth=The Eye Of Eternity-Supreme Center=Omniscience
    and Omnipresence
---
With the mind thus composed, quite purified, quite clarified, without blemish,
without defilement, grown soft and workable, fixed, immovable. I directed
my mind to the knowledge and recollection of former habitations. ... Thus
I remember divers former habitations in all their modes and details.
